The Crime Tracer -- `Changelog' starts here.

Changelog:

2010-12-05  Sakis Kasampalis <faif@dtek.gr>
	* Refactored all files to be python 3 compatible.

2009-10-11  Efstathios Xatzikiriakidis  <contact@efxa.org>

    * intro.py (Intro): Add class for intro screen implementation.
    * cut_scenes.py (CutScenes): Add class for cut scenes action.

2009-09-13  Efstathios Xatzikiriakidis  <contact@efxa.org>

    * *.py: Perform all PEP 8 instructions.
    * menu.py (Menu_Screen): Rename class to `Menu'.
    * credits.py (Credits_Screen): Rename class to `Credits'.

2009-09-11  Efstathios Xatzikiriakidis  <contact@efxa.org>

	* menu.py (menu_settings): Display the menu settings list
      always in the middle of the window screen regardless of
      the resolution of the game.

2009-09-10  Efstathios Xatzikiriakidis  <contact@efxa.org>

	* credits.py (Credits): Improve the parser in the constructor
      of the Credits class. Parse now can accept more token, tags
      and ignores any comment lines.

The Crime Tracer -- `Changelog' ends here.
